flowchart LR
    A[Ad hoc] --> S[Standardized]
    S --> T[Trusted]
    T --> E[Experimental]
    E --> AD[Adaptive]

    A1[Local dashboards and inconsistent definitions] -.-> A
    S1[Canonical events, catalogue, published principles] -.-> S
    T1[Lineage, corrections, privacy, participation] -.-> T
    E1[Registered experiments and causal evaluation] -.-> E
    AD1[Validated policies, monitoring, retirement, rollback] -.-> AD
